This project focuses on cleaning, standardizing, and preparing customer
contact data for analysis or operational use. 
Using Python and Pandas, the notebook transforms a
raw customer call list into a clean, structured,
and reliable dataset by addressing common data quality 
issues found in real-world business data.

The project demonstrates essential data preprocessing skills
required for data analysis, CRM systems,
and reporting workflows.
