ğŸ” Data Cleaning & Transformation Steps

The notebook performs the following operations:

Removing duplicate customer records

Dropping irrelevant or unused columns

Cleaning last name fields by removing unwanted characters

Standardizing phone numbers:

Removing non-numeric characters

Formatting phone numbers consistently

Splitting address data into:

Street Address

State

Zip Code

Standardizing categorical values (e.g., No â†’ N)
Handling missing and invalid values

Removing customers marked as Do Not Contact

Removing records without valid phone numbers

Resetting and reindexing the final dataset

ğŸ“ˆ Final Output

The resulting dataset:

Contains only valid, contactable customers

Uses consistent formatting across all columns

